context:
KR:
&lt;지금 무슨 소리를…&gt;
EN:
&lt;What are you...&gt;

KR:
&lt;그건…&gt;
EN:
&lt;That's...&gt;

KR:
&lt;그래서… 뭐, 어떡하라는 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;So... what the hell do you want me to do?&gt;

KR:
&lt;허. 나도 순간 솔깃해지네.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Huh. I guess that makes... some sense.&gt;

KR:
&lt;전해줘, 파우스트.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Tell her what I'm about to say, Faust.&gt;

KR:
&lt;당신은 수감자들을 책임져 주지 않을 거야.&gt;
EN:
&lt;You're not going to be responsible for the Sinners.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그리고 내 머리가 부서지면 수감자들이 어떻게 될지는 아무도 몰라.&gt;
EN:
&lt;And no one knows what'll happen to the Sinners if my head is crushed.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그런 불확실한 것에 모두와의 미래를 맡길 수 없어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;I'm not going to let the doubts you cast chart our futures.&gt;

KR:
&lt;나는 관리자니까.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Because I am their Manager.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그리고… 나는 죽기 싫어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Besides... I don't want to die.&gt;
